data.description: This is your opportunity to live in the sought after Grande Park Clubhouse Community. Discover this stunning 5-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom residence set on a 1/3 acre fenced-in yard. This home boasts an updated kitchen with Brakur Custom Cabinetry, Dior White quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances (2023), a spacious family room with a fireplace, and hardwood floors gracing the entire first floor. Elegance abounds the dual staircases, a formal living and dining room with butler's station, and a main level office for work or study. There are five spacious bedrooms each with WIC and access to private bathrooms.  Step outside to a large paved brick patio featuring an Oahu Tropical Seas Spa (2020), perfect for relaxation with green space and walking trails behind the fenced in yard. The home is equipped with dual zoned heating(2005), OXY 4 air purifiers (2022), dual zoned A/C units (2018/2022), two water heaters (2022), and new privacy fence (2022). Enjoy an array of amenities in the Grande Park clubhouse including the  pool, tennis courts, parks, and playground in this community. Please exclude all drapes/curtains. Trampoline is staying. Fall in love with your dream home and buy with confidence.
